    <h2>Architectural Standards (ASC)</h2>
    <div class="About">
        <p>The Semiahmoo Resort Association has architectural standards in order to preserve the natural setting and beauty of the resort and to establish and preserve a harmonious and aesthetically pleasing design for our community.</p>
    </div>

