    <section class= "sub-committees-container">
      <h2>Communications</h2>
      <div class="About"><p>The Communications Committee, chaired by a Board Member of the Semiahmoo Resort Association, Inc. shall have the dual responsibility of (1) keeping the community accurately informed of Association activities and (2) supporting the Mission, Vision and Values of the Association. The Committee shall also assist the Board by communicating current and planned actions being considered by the Board, or other activities of community interest. The Committee shall also be responsible for developing and maintaining channels of outbound and inbound communication between the Board, its various committees, and the Residents</p></div>
