    <section class= "sub-committees-container">
      <h2>Safety and Security</h2>
      <div class="About">
      <p>The Safety and Security Committee (S&SC), chaired by a Board Member of the Semiahmoo Resort Association, (SRA), shall assist the Board in fulfilling its Duty of Care to the membership by providing oversight of the safety and security activities of the community. The S&SC may make recommendations to the Board for Board approval, modification or rejection of new or existing policies or procedures. Such recommendations shall include consideration of future needs and expectations consistent with the mission and vision of the SRA.</p></div>
      <section class= "sub-committee-row">
