      <h2>Maintenance</h2>
      <div class="About">
      <p>The Maintenance Committee (MC) shall assist the Semiahmoo Residents Association (SRA) Board of Directors (Board) in fulfilling its obligation to provide oversight of the condition & maintenance of SRA property and other property where SRA has maintenance responsibilities as specified by SRA and Neighborhood HOA (NHOA) CC&Rs.</p></div>
